'''迈瑞医疗国际有限公司'''，簡稱'''深圳邁瑞醫療'''，是一家位于中国[[深圳|深圳]]的全球性[[医疗器械|医疗器械]]开发商、制造商、销售商。迈瑞设计和生产各种医疗器械、设备、人类和兽类医用附属设备。公司现由三个关键商业线构成：病人监护与生命维持、[[In_vitro|In vitro]]产品和[[医学影像|医学影像]]系统。2008年，迈瑞被认证为中国最大的医疗器械制造商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bg2.mofcom.gov.cn/aarticle/supplydemandofchina/cooperation/200509/20050900369369.html|title=China's Largest Medical Device Manufacturer|access-date=2008-02-04|archive-date=2008-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226035003/http://bg2.mofcom.gov.cn/aarticle/supplydemandofchina/cooperation/200509/20050900369369.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
迈瑞于1991在中国深圳由包括李西廷、徐航和成明和的七名[[安科生物|安科生物]]前雇员创立。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cj.sina.com.cn/article/detail/6066470577/188555|title=中国合伙人：迈瑞三剑客创业史|date=2017-03-15|website=Sina|access-date=2019-05-10|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116234535/https://cj.sina.com.cn/article/detail/6066470577/188555|dead-url=no}}</ref>它通过提供国内患者监测、成像和其他诊断产品而成长，从此成为一家领先的全球制造商。迈瑞在31个国家保有41家子公司和分支机构，在中国有32家分公司。迈瑞于2006年9月跻身[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]，2016年3月为了重新申请跻身中国[[A股_(中国)|A股]]而退出。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mindray-medical-international|title=Mindray Medical International|website=Crunchbase|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2019-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510220336/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mindray-medical-international|dead-url=no}}</ref>迈瑞于2018年10月又被列入[[深圳证券交易所|深圳证券交易所]]。

2018年底，迈瑞因经济状况变化而取消了来自254名大学生的工作邀请，引发了招聘争议。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2180796/how-chinas-worsening-economic-woes-are-shattering-dreams-its|title=How China’s economic woes are smashing its top graduates’ dreams|date=7 January 2019|website=South China Morning Post|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308103617/https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2180796/how-chinas-worsening-economic-woes-are-shattering-dreams-its|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年初其在公众强烈抗议后引用“企业社会责任”恢复了这些邀请。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2181400/youre-rehired-chinese-firm-overturns-decision-cancel|title=You’re rehired! Chinese firm restores job offers to over 200 graduates|date=9 January 2019|website=South China Morning Post|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107234548/https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2181400/youre-rehired-chinese-firm-overturns-decision-cancel|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年1月迈瑞与Korle Bu教学医院合作改善[[加纳|加纳]]的诊断患者护理。该公司捐赠了一台SAL6000分析仪以提高当地实验室的测试效率。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businessghana.com/site/news/general/180798/Korle-Bu-Hospital-inaugurates-state-of-the-art-analyzer-laboratory|title=Korle-Bu Hospital inaugurates state-of-the-art analyzer laboratory|website=BusinessGhana|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813051432/https://www.businessghana.com/site/news/general/180798/Korle-Bu-Hospital-inaugurates-state-of-the-art-analyzer-laboratory|dead-url=no}}</ref>

